title: Super Junior Full House
overview: Two female international students - Anya, a 20-year old Russian intern, and Eva, a 25-year old half-Japanese half-English intern - arrive in Seoul, South Korea to do a home stay with half the members of Super Junior. While living with Super Junior, the two foreign students experience comedic adventures with the group and develop deep friendships. A comedy, these thirteen episodes center mostly around Super Junior learning English.
